52:03.560 --> 52:04.740
and break your hand,

52:05.080 --> 52:05.940
but program it

52:05.940 --> 52:07.000
to recognize you

52:07.000 --> 52:08.280
and open sesame.

52:09.340 --> 52:10.340
They're essentially

52:10.340 --> 52:11.500
programmable matter,

52:11.900 --> 52:13.020
solid or permeable

52:13.020 --> 52:13.740
on demand.

52:14.260 --> 52:14.880
They could fake

52:14.880 --> 52:15.600
the gritty feel

52:15.600 --> 52:16.380
