52:16.380 --> 52:17.180
and layered rock

52:17.180 --> 52:18.140
by dialing in

52:18.140 --> 52:18.840
just the right

52:18.840 --> 52:19.840
micro-vibrations

52:19.840 --> 52:20.580
for your skin

52:20.580 --> 52:22.060
to read as solid stone.

52:22.280 --> 52:23.140
But there's a catch.

