run the foglets

52:41.780 --> 52:42.580
in pixel mode,

52:42.580 --> 52:43.860
and the outer skin

52:43.860 --> 52:44.920
basically becomes

52:44.920 --> 52:46.480
a 3D TV screen,

52:46.960 --> 52:47.680
blending into

52:47.680 --> 52:48.920
whatever you want it to.

52:49.500 --> 52:50.200
Now look at how

52:50.200 --> 52:51.280
the story describes

52:51.280 --> 52:52.300
the mountain's behavior.

52:52.960 --> 52:54.360
That's our next big tell

52:54.360 --> 52:55.380
that we might not be

52:55.380 --> 52:55.960
dealing with

52:55.960 --> 52:57.020
a simple hologram.

52:57.300 --> 52:58.060
As the helicopters

52:58.060 --> 52:59.240
are about to collide

52:59.240 --> 53:00.280
with the mountainside,

53:00.740 --> 53:01.920
its 3D appearance

53:01.920 --> 53:03.340
transitions to 2D,

53:03.660 --> 53:04.780
then pixelates

53:04.780 --> 53:05.460
into nothing.

53:05.940 --> 53:07.260
If upgraded foglets

53:07.260 --> 53:07.840
exist,

53:08.380 --> 53:09.820
and that is a big if,

53:10.020 --> 53:10.580
we are admittedly

53:10.580 --> 53:12.600
engaging in extreme

53:12.600 --> 53:13.640
speculation here.

53:13.840 --> 53:14.720
So you should accept

53:14.720 --> 53:15.540
that caveat.

53:16.200 --> 53:17.340
But if they exist,

53:17.680 --> 53:18.800
this is the behavior

53:18.800 --> 53:20.260
you might expect to see.

53:20.520 --> 53:22.120
As the helicopters close in,

53:22.300 --> 53:23.180
foglets would start

53:23.180 --> 53:24.260
shifting formation,

53:24.920 --> 53:25.700
half their arms

53:25.700 --> 53:26.340
staying locked

53:26.340 --> 53:27.420
in lattice formation,

53:27.620 --> 53:28.280
while the rest

53:28.280 --> 53:29.900
drop out of rock mode

53:29.900 --> 53:31.240
as the mountainside

53:31.240 --> 53:32.540
dissolves into flickering

53:32.540 --> 53:33.740
patches like pixels

53:33.740 --> 53:34.580
on a screen.

53:34.840 --> 53:35.680
From the cockpit,

53:35.940 --> 53:36.620
it would look like

53:36.620 --> 53:37.720
a 3D mountainside,

53:37.900 --> 53:39.120
flattening into a weird,

53:39.120 --> 53:40.560
shimmering 2D skin

53:40.560 --> 53:42.240
that breaks into pixels

53:42.240 --> 53:43.440
and dissolves

53:43.440 --> 53:44.300
as the helicopter

53:44.300 --> 53:45.160
passes through.

53:45.480 --> 53:46.940
The low-frequency pulsing

53:46.940 --> 53:48.020
in the crew's headsets

53:48.020 --> 53:48.960
is another clue.

53:49.200 --> 53:50.580
It's not ambient sound,

53:50.880 --> 53:51.940
so one possibility

53:51.940 --> 53:53.680
is strong radio frequency

53:53.680 --> 53:54.680
emissions bleeding

53:54.680 --> 53:56.000
into their radio gear,

53:56.180 --> 53:57.380
a glitch that's known

53:57.380 --> 53:58.800
as audio rectification.

53:59.060 --> 54:00.780
If foglets were adapted

54:00.780 --> 54:01.860
for the real world,

54:02.200 --> 54:03.580
they'd likely be upgraded

54:03.580 --> 54:04.740
with wireless,

54:04.940 --> 54:06.060
real-time communication

54:06.060 --> 54:07.680
for swarm coordination.

54:07.680 --> 54:09.260
So imagine trillions

54:09.260 --> 54:10.440
of foglets moving

54:10.440 --> 54:11.760
in coordinated waves,

54:12.140 --> 54:13.220
unlocking, shifting

54:13.220 --> 54:14.080
antenna arms,

54:14.280 --> 54:15.100
and cycling their

54:15.100 --> 54:16.080
electrical states.

54:16.460 --> 54:17.480
That kind of swarm

54:17.480 --> 54:18.140
could generate

54:18.140 --> 54:19.540
the strong radio emissions

54:19.540 --> 54:21.600
and an audible pulsing

54:21.600 --> 54:22.960
you'd hear in your headset.

54:23.440 --> 54:24.540
A hologram wouldn't

54:24.540 --> 54:25.500
do any of this.

54:26.780 --> 54:28.260
Remember, in the novel,

54:28.460 --> 54:30.120
the drone and the F-18s

54:30.120 --> 54:31.360
suddenly lose power,

54:31.740 --> 54:32.840
while the helicopters

54:32.840 --> 54:34.060
slip right through

54:34.060 --> 54:35.340
the mountain, untouched.

54:35.340 --> 54:37.260
In theory, if the mountain

54:37.260 --> 54:38.540
is really a trillion

54:38.540 --> 54:39.560
little foglets,

54:39.960 --> 54:41.660
each spec with its own brain,

54:41.980 --> 54:43.380
sensors, and comms,

54:43.800 --> 54:45.140
they could act like a living

54:45.140 --> 54:47.260
electromagnetic warfare system.

54:47.840 --> 54:49.220
With each cubic inch

54:49.220 --> 54:51.440
packing 16 million processors,

54:51.980 --> 54:52.640
they could jam

54:52.640 --> 54:53.900
specific signals,

54:54.480 --> 54:55.840
bleed power from drones

54:55.840 --> 54:57.660
while leaving others untouched,

54:58.080 --> 54:59.880
and run friend or foe codes

54:59.880 --> 55:01.800
so only approved aircraft

55:01.800 --> 55:03.120
get a clean pass.

55:03.120 --> 55:04.540
returning helicopters

55:04.540 --> 55:06.260
could transmit the right codes

55:06.260 --> 55:07.140
to slip through,

55:07.600 --> 55:08.660
giving everyone else

55:08.660 --> 55:09.440
power failure

55:09.440 --> 55:11.320
and a not-so-gentle escort

55:11.320 --> 55:12.160
into the dirt.

55:12.620 --> 55:13.440
Now, this mountain

55:13.440 --> 55:14.660
in Sentinels of Aether

55:14.660 --> 55:16.360
could also be pure fiction.

55:16.760 --> 55:18.000
But crafts vanishing

55:18.000 --> 55:18.800
into mountains

55:18.800 --> 55:20.380
is a documented phenomenon,

55:20.900 --> 55:22.120
especially in places

55:22.120 --> 55:23.400
like the Uinta Basin.

55:23.400 --> 55:27.600
If something lets objects

55:27.600 --> 55:28.600
slip through

55:28.600 --> 55:30.280
what looks like solid rock,

55:30.540 --> 55:31.900
we're probably beyond

55:31.900 --> 55:33.160
conventional technology

55:33.160 --> 55:34.320
and already playing

55:34.320 --> 55:35.900
in the Black World sandbox.

55:36.280 --> 55:37.980
Foglets are just my best guess,

55:38.160 --> 55:39.000
but they aren't some

55:39.000 --> 55:40.640
wild stoner fantasy either.

55:41.320 --> 55:43.260
The DIA has openly mused

55:43.260 --> 55:44.520
about programmable matter

55:44.520 --> 55:46.320
for camouflage and invisibility.

55:46.320 --> 55:51.200
In the 1990s to 2000s,

55:51.260 --> 55:52.860
the idea of smart dust

55:52.860 --> 55:54.260
caught fire among

55:54.260 --> 55:55.880
sci-fi nerds everywhere,

55:56.140 --> 55:57.940
including some feds at DARPA

55:57.940 --> 55:59.440
who began funding research

55:59.440 --> 56:00.640
on millimeter-scale

56:00.640 --> 56:01.860
autonomous sensing

56:01.860 --> 56:03.400
and communication nodes.

56:03.740 --> 56:04.820
While utility fog

56:04.820 --> 56:06.000
is still theoretical,

56:06.260 --> 56:07.100
the building blocks

56:07.100 --> 56:08.660
were active research areas

56:08.660 --> 56:09.400
back then.

56:09.600 --> 56:10.440
By 2001,

56:10.780 --> 56:11.900
DARPA was demonstrating

56:11.900 --> 56:13.760
smart dust in field tests.

56:13.760 --> 56:16.340
By 2004, MEMS,

56:16.560 --> 56:18.480
or Microelectromechanical Systems

56:18.480 --> 56:19.160
technology,

56:19.420 --> 56:20.980
had matured significantly.

56:21.260 --> 56:22.240
Publicly, we know

56:22.240 --> 56:23.660
about DARPA's smart dust

56:23.660 --> 56:25.040
and creepy biohybrid

56:25.040 --> 56:26.220
insect cyborgs,

56:26.760 --> 56:27.700
but in the Black World,

56:27.840 --> 56:28.940
we have no idea

56:28.940 --> 56:29.900
what exists.

56:30.400 --> 56:31.260
Hall himself,

56:31.540 --> 56:32.400
again the creator

56:32.400 --> 56:33.340
of this concept,

56:33.640 --> 56:34.540
has warned that

56:34.540 --> 56:35.340
a lot of the work

56:35.340 --> 56:36.900
needed for real nanotech

56:36.900 --> 56:38.460
got actively suppressed,

56:39.020 --> 56:39.840
which is why we're

56:39.840 --> 56:40.560
a bit behind

56:40.560 --> 56:42.020
on Star Trek replicators

56:42.020 --> 56:43.260
and nano assemblers.

56:43.260 --> 56:44.760
And let's not forget

56:44.760 --> 56:46.480
about the Invention Secrecy Act

56:46.480 --> 56:47.640
of 1951.

56:47.900 --> 56:48.880
This lets Uncle Sam

56:48.880 --> 56:50.140
classify and bury

56:50.140 --> 56:50.880
both government

56:50.880 --> 56:52.020
and private inventions,

56:52.620 --> 56:54.200
including patent applications

56:54.200 --> 56:54.940
in the name

56:54.940 --> 56:56.040
of national security.

56:56.300 --> 56:56.940
If something like

56:56.940 --> 56:58.260
utility fog exists

56:58.260 --> 56:59.700
in a classified program,

57:00.180 --> 57:01.140
filing a patent

57:01.140 --> 57:02.580
would amount to disclosure.

57:03.080 --> 57:03.880
So there's a reason

57:03.880 --> 57:05.020
no patents exist.

57:05.240 --> 57:05.820
The whole point

57:05.820 --> 57:06.940
of special access programs

57:06.940 --> 57:07.580
is to keep

57:07.580 --> 57:08.800
these capabilities hidden.

57:09.060 --> 57:10.040
You wouldn't telegraph

57:10.040 --> 57:10.760
that you've solved

57:10.760 --> 57:12.180
molecular nanotechnology.

57:12.180 --> 57:13.640
If you want to keep

57:13.640 --> 57:14.540
something a secret,

57:14.760 --> 57:15.560
you don't file.

57:16.000 --> 57:16.820
And then you have

57:16.820 --> 57:17.540
Ben Rich,

57:17.720 --> 57:18.620
former head of

57:18.620 --> 57:19.560
Lockheed Skunk Works,

57:19.700 --> 57:20.720
saying things like,

57:21.140 --> 57:22.320
we already have the means

57:22.320 --> 57:23.820
to travel among the stars,

57:24.180 --> 57:25.280
but these technologies

57:25.280 --> 57:26.200
are locked up

57:26.200 --> 57:27.180
in black projects

57:27.180 --> 57:27.960
and it would take

57:27.960 --> 57:29.100
an act of God

57:29.100 --> 57:30.500
to ever get them out

57:30.500 --> 57:31.540
to benefit humanity.

57:32.080 --> 57:33.300
Anything you can imagine,

57:33.520 --> 57:34.300
we already know

57:34.300 --> 57:35.100
how to do.

57:35.740 --> 57:36.800
Rich even claimed,

57:36.960 --> 57:37.940
we have things out

57:37.940 --> 57:38.520
in the desert

57:38.520 --> 57:39.880
that are 50 years

57:39.880 --> 57:40.640
beyond what you

57:40.640 --> 57:41.820
could possibly comprehend.

57:42.320 --> 57:43.000
If you've seen it

57:43.000 --> 57:43.840
on Star Wars

57:43.840 --> 57:44.740
or Star Trek,

57:44.900 --> 57:45.600
we've been there

57:45.600 --> 57:46.400
and done that.

57:46.660 --> 57:47.560
He also admitted

57:47.560 --> 57:48.480
that there are people

57:48.480 --> 57:49.780
in the intelligence world

57:49.780 --> 57:50.640
who want this

57:50.640 --> 57:51.740
breakthrough technology

57:51.740 --> 57:53.540
to stay in the black forever.

57:53.860 --> 57:54.700
And he's saying this

57:54.700 --> 57:55.580
in 1995,

57:56.060 --> 57:56.920
the same era

57:56.920 --> 57:57.820
Hall is pitching

57:57.820 --> 57:59.320
utility fog to NASA.

57:59.620 --> 58:00.680
So if Rich is right,

58:00.780 --> 58:02.260
then by the early 2000s,

58:02.320 --> 58:03.220
the public was still

58:03.220 --> 58:04.540
gawking at smart dust

58:04.540 --> 58:05.800
while some special access

58:05.800 --> 58:06.580
program buried

58:06.580 --> 58:07.280
in the desert

58:07.280 --> 58:08.540
might have been playing

58:08.540 --> 58:09.360
with full-blown

58:09.360 --> 58:10.440
programmable matter,

58:10.880 --> 58:11.660
the kind of tech

58:11.660 --> 58:12.660
that could absolutely

58:12.660 --> 58:13.600
fake a mountain.

58:14.060 --> 58:14.940
Just look at what

58:14.940 --> 58:15.760
Ross Coulthart

58:15.760 --> 58:16.680
and his sources

58:16.680 --> 58:17.380
have said

58:17.380 --> 58:18.860
about Bradshaw Ranch

58:18.860 --> 58:19.700
in Arizona.

58:19.920 --> 58:20.520
There is a portal

58:20.520 --> 58:21.600
in the United States.

58:21.720 --> 58:21.920
In fact,

58:21.960 --> 58:22.980
I suspect there are multiple.

58:23.600 --> 58:24.840
But this particular portal

58:24.840 --> 58:26.840
is in a highly guarded facility

58:26.840 --> 58:27.600
that is used

58:27.600 --> 58:29.380
under the U.S. Forest Service cover.

58:30.320 --> 58:31.200
There are men

58:31.200 --> 58:31.800
with guns

58:31.800 --> 58:32.660
who patrol it

58:32.660 --> 58:34.040
and there are witnesses

58:34.040 --> 58:35.240
who have seen

58:35.240 --> 58:36.900
people walking

58:36.900 --> 58:38.780
into literally

58:38.780 --> 58:39.680
a wall.

58:40.360 --> 58:41.320
So we have craft

58:41.320 --> 58:42.520
moving in and out

58:42.520 --> 58:43.060
of a mountain.

58:43.220 --> 58:44.140
We even have people

58:44.140 --> 58:45.520
walking through walls.

58:45.940 --> 58:47.460
Now let's talk psionics,

58:47.700 --> 58:48.860
the psychic summoning

58:48.860 --> 58:49.880
of UFOs,

58:50.280 --> 58:51.800
Jake Barber's secret sauce.

58:51.980 --> 58:52.600
We're told,

58:52.760 --> 58:53.640
and there's a whole movie

58:53.640 --> 58:54.260
made about it,

58:54.420 --> 58:55.400
debunking the idea

58:55.400 --> 58:56.160
of telepathy

58:56.160 --> 58:56.860
and psychics

58:56.860 --> 58:57.560
and psionics.

58:57.740 --> 58:58.720
And yet you've only

58:58.720 --> 58:59.300
got to read

58:59.300 --> 59:01.720
the CIA gateway documents

59:01.720 --> 59:02.920
in the CIA files

59:02.920 --> 59:03.760
and they show that

59:03.760 --> 59:05.260
that's actually not true.

59:05.360 --> 59:05.620
Yes.

59:05.780 --> 59:06.720
That essentially

59:06.720 --> 59:08.840
everybody took it

59:08.840 --> 59:09.960
very, very seriously.

59:10.780 --> 59:12.520
Jake Barber told Herrera

59:12.520 --> 59:13.980
that the paramilitary unit

59:13.980 --> 59:14.580
he encountered

59:14.580 --> 59:15.620
was transporting

59:15.620 --> 59:16.980
psionic assets,

59:17.700 --> 59:18.740
people with special

59:18.740 --> 59:19.840
intuitive abilities.

59:20.180 --> 59:21.020
What is real

59:21.020 --> 59:22.540
is the ability

59:22.540 --> 59:24.420
to go into something

59:24.420 --> 59:25.720
like a meditative state

59:25.720 --> 59:27.420
and summon UAP

59:27.420 --> 59:29.120
and pilot UAP.

59:29.600 --> 59:30.460
That is real.

59:30.540 --> 59:31.340
That's 100% real.

59:32.300 --> 59:32.780
Wow.

59:32.780 --> 59:34.480
I have to process

59:34.480 --> 59:35.180
that for a moment

59:35.180 --> 59:36.020
because that is just

59:36.020 --> 59:37.400
the most extraordinary claim.

59:37.560 --> 59:39.200
He calls them P3s

59:39.200 --> 59:42.260
or psionic predisposition potential.

59:42.580 --> 59:43.180
These aren't

59:43.180 --> 59:44.440
your average recruits.

59:44.840 --> 59:45.960
He personally sees it

59:45.960 --> 59:47.160
less like human trafficking

59:47.160 --> 59:48.820
and more like elite recruitment

59:48.820 --> 59:50.520
into specialized programs.

59:50.880 --> 59:52.020
Although admittedly,

59:52.120 --> 59:53.580
reading a lot of these stories

59:53.580 --> 59:55.120
makes me pretty concerned

59:55.120 --> 59:56.960
about human rights violations.

59:57.800 --> 59:59.640
So when these P3s

59:59.640 --> 01:00:00.760
or psionic assets

01:00:00.760 --> 01:00:01.460
are recruited,

01:00:01.680 --> 01:00:03.020
what do they actually do?

01:00:03.420 --> 01:00:04.580
Jake describes them

01:00:04.580 --> 01:00:05.760
as intuitives,

01:00:06.140 --> 01:00:07.260
trained like assets

01:00:07.260 --> 01:00:08.200
in remote viewing,

01:00:08.580 --> 01:00:09.440
telekinesis,

01:00:09.660 --> 01:00:11.240
and the whole psychic toolkit.

01:00:11.460 --> 01:00:12.460
All of this is honed

01:00:12.460 --> 01:00:14.040
through specific protocols.

01:00:14.460 --> 01:00:15.720
Their job is to tap

01:00:15.720 --> 01:00:16.820
into what he calls

01:00:16.820 --> 01:00:18.160
the consciousness field.

01:00:18.880 --> 01:00:19.340
Think of it

01:00:19.340 --> 01:00:20.100
like a cosmic

01:00:20.100 --> 01:00:21.220
worldwide web,

01:00:21.600 --> 01:00:22.660
full of information

01:00:22.660 --> 01:00:23.440
everywhere,

01:00:23.840 --> 01:00:24.640
all the time,

01:00:25.080 --> 01:00:25.480
invisible

01:00:25.480 --> 01:00:27.060
until you access it.

01:00:27.060 --> 01:00:28.740
A P3 is the receiver,

01:00:29.200 --> 01:00:30.160
the Wi-Fi antenna.

01:00:30.480 --> 01:00:31.400
According to Jake,

01:00:31.560 --> 01:00:32.500
there are two main

01:00:32.500 --> 01:00:33.560
attraction methods.

01:00:33.860 --> 01:00:35.200
Machine-based systems,

01:00:35.600 --> 01:00:37.140
signals or energy systems

01:00:37.140 --> 01:00:38.380
that act like a beacon

01:00:38.380 --> 01:00:39.440
or dog whistle.

01:00:39.660 --> 01:00:40.660
After we turn on

01:00:40.660 --> 01:00:41.280
the dog whistle,

01:00:41.720 --> 01:00:43.420
UAPs literally come to us

01:00:43.420 --> 01:00:44.400
day after day.

01:00:45.060 --> 01:00:46.660
Or our manned-based systems,

01:00:46.920 --> 01:00:47.960
trained psionics

01:00:47.960 --> 01:00:49.520
projecting an invitation

01:00:49.520 --> 01:00:50.500
through the field,

01:00:50.980 --> 01:00:52.300
essentially calling to

01:00:52.300 --> 01:00:53.800
whatever's monitoring it.

01:00:54.160 --> 01:00:55.820
To train a psionic asset,

01:00:55.820 --> 01:00:57.060
you have to shut down

01:00:57.060 --> 01:00:58.240
the overthinking brain

01:00:58.240 --> 01:01:00.140
and let intuition run point.

01:01:00.560 --> 01:01:01.680
Children are naturally

01:01:01.680 --> 01:01:02.420
better at this

01:01:02.420 --> 01:01:03.240
since they're usually

01:01:03.240 --> 01:01:03.940
more intuitive.

01:01:04.500 --> 01:01:05.440
Basically the plot

01:01:05.440 --> 01:01:06.480
of Stranger Things,

01:01:06.960 --> 01:01:08.500
psychic kids being tested

01:01:08.500 --> 01:01:10.020
at Department of Energy

01:01:10.020 --> 01:01:11.140
National Labs.

01:01:11.680 --> 01:01:13.140
Jake's consciousness-based

01:01:13.140 --> 01:01:14.120
attraction method

01:01:14.120 --> 01:01:15.160
is very similar

01:01:15.160 --> 01:01:16.360
to Stephen Greer's

01:01:16.360 --> 01:01:17.740
coherent thought sequencing,

01:01:18.120 --> 01:01:18.960
the core technique

01:01:18.960 --> 01:01:20.680
in his CE5 protocol.

01:01:21.120 --> 01:01:22.520
It's a meditation-based

01:01:22.520 --> 01:01:23.980
invitation system

01:01:23.980 --> 01:01:25.780
built on a similar premise,

01:01:26.120 --> 01:01:27.300
consciousness as a

01:01:27.300 --> 01:01:28.280
communication channel.

01:01:28.420 --> 01:01:29.220
Now I know Greer

01:01:29.220 --> 01:01:30.260
can be polarizing.

01:01:30.720 --> 01:01:31.680
At times he can be

01:01:31.680 --> 01:01:32.640
self-aggrandizing

01:01:32.640 --> 01:01:33.780
and just plain wrong

01:01:33.780 --> 01:01:34.840
about a whole lot.

01:01:35.380 --> 01:01:36.060
But he's stayed

01:01:36.060 --> 01:01:37.300
remarkably consistent

01:01:37.300 --> 01:01:38.380
on this one thing

01:01:38.380 --> 01:01:39.060
for decades.

