01:10:05.860 --> 01:10:07.380
a helmet with which

01:10:07.380 --> 01:10:08.120
you could steer

01:10:08.120 --> 01:10:09.720
a UFO with your mind.

01:10:09.840 --> 01:10:11.400
The fact that the UFOs

01:10:11.400 --> 01:10:12.840
appear to be navigated

01:10:12.840 --> 01:10:13.700
telepathically,

01:10:13.840 --> 01:10:14.680
for example,

01:10:15.060 --> 01:10:16.800
and that the craft

01:10:16.800 --> 01:10:17.800
have built into it

01:10:17.800 --> 01:10:19.460
some kind of an AI capacity

01:10:19.460 --> 01:10:21.380
to respond telepathically

01:10:21.380 --> 01:10:22.160
to the control

01:10:22.160 --> 01:10:23.140
of the pilot.

01:10:23.360 --> 01:10:25.080
Now that's pretty far out.

01:10:25.660 --> 01:10:26.480
Thanks to leaps

01:10:26.480 --> 01:10:27.960
in data signal technology,

01:10:28.320 --> 01:10:29.540
it might be reality.

01:10:30.040 --> 01:10:31.540
For Lockheed's Don Phillips,

01:10:31.700 --> 01:10:33.060
it's proof that technology

01:10:33.060 --> 01:10:34.440
is finally catching up

01:10:34.440 --> 01:10:35.180
to the fastest,

01:10:35.400 --> 01:10:36.660
most powerful processor

01:10:36.660 --> 01:10:37.680
in existence,

01:10:38.360 --> 01:10:39.380
the human mind,

01:10:39.620 --> 01:10:40.780
on certain dimensions

01:10:40.780 --> 01:10:41.960
involving intuition,

01:10:42.220 --> 01:10:43.460
still miles ahead

01:10:43.460 --> 01:10:45.300
of any machine ever built,

01:10:45.300 --> 01:10:47.220
even with large language models.

01:10:49.140 --> 01:10:50.780
So one Lockheed insider

01:10:50.780 --> 01:10:51.860
calls the human body

01:10:51.860 --> 01:10:52.580
a supercomputer

01:10:52.580 --> 01:10:54.260
that can command aircraft

01:10:54.260 --> 01:10:54.840
with thought,

01:10:55.080 --> 01:10:56.160
while another says

01:10:56.160 --> 01:10:57.060
exotic propulsion

01:10:57.060 --> 01:10:58.400
works like ESP.

01:10:59.120 --> 01:10:59.680
Suddenly,

01:10:59.900 --> 01:11:00.480
Jake's story

01:11:00.480 --> 01:11:01.840
doesn't sound so crazy.

01:11:03.860 --> 01:11:05.260
But there's more proof

01:11:05.260 --> 01:11:05.860
Jake Barber

01:11:05.860 --> 01:11:07.080
isn't out of his mind.

01:11:07.280 --> 01:11:08.220
His story would have made

01:11:08.220 --> 01:11:09.240
a lot of sense

01:11:09.240 --> 01:11:10.340
to John Norseen,

01:11:10.580 --> 01:11:11.860
a former Navy pilot

01:11:11.860 --> 01:11:13.480
turned neuroengineer

01:11:13.480 --> 01:11:14.740
and weapons designer

01:11:14.740 --> 01:11:15.780
for Lockheed Martin.

01:11:16.200 --> 01:11:16.820
This is a man

01:11:16.820 --> 01:11:18.160
who is funded by NASA

01:11:18.160 --> 01:11:18.940
and DARPA

01:11:18.940 --> 01:11:20.940
for mind-reading research.

01:11:21.280 --> 01:11:22.220
In 1999,

01:11:22.760 --> 01:11:23.660
Norseen published

01:11:23.660 --> 01:11:25.380
a report on biofusion,

01:11:25.580 --> 01:11:27.160
a system he later described

01:11:27.160 --> 01:11:29.420
involving brain-computer interfaces

01:11:29.420 --> 01:11:31.100
that convert thoughts

01:11:31.100 --> 01:11:32.280
into commands.

01:11:32.660 --> 01:11:33.800
No joystick or buttons.

01:11:34.100 --> 01:11:34.940
You just think

01:11:34.940 --> 01:11:36.660
and the aircraft moves.

01:11:37.160 --> 01:11:38.140
According to a man

01:11:38.140 --> 01:11:39.620
named Doug Pasternak

01:11:39.620 --> 01:11:40.840
who interacted with him,

01:11:41.040 --> 01:11:41.920
Norseen believed

01:11:41.920 --> 01:11:42.680
that a pilot

01:11:42.680 --> 01:11:43.800
could fly a plane

01:11:43.800 --> 01:11:45.140
by merely thinking.

01:11:45.520 --> 01:11:45.900
Basically,

01:11:46.060 --> 01:11:46.600
no delay,

01:11:46.940 --> 01:11:47.680
no latency.

01:11:48.420 --> 01:11:48.880
For example,

01:11:49.000 --> 01:11:49.480
when you say

01:11:49.480 --> 01:11:50.860
write 090 degrees,

01:11:51.180 --> 01:11:52.100
the computer maps

01:11:52.100 --> 01:11:53.760
the pilot's electrical pattern

01:11:53.760 --> 01:11:54.480
in the brain

01:11:54.480 --> 01:11:55.700
and turns the pilot

01:11:55.700 --> 01:11:57.140
090 degrees.

01:11:58.140 --> 01:11:59.520
And if there's a mistake

01:11:59.520 --> 01:12:00.180
and the pilot

01:12:00.180 --> 01:12:02.220
processes 080 degrees,

01:12:02.600 --> 01:12:03.080
the helmet

01:12:03.080 --> 01:12:04.240
catches the mistake

01:12:04.240 --> 01:12:05.240
and injects

01:12:05.240 --> 01:12:06.040
the right number

01:12:06.040 --> 01:12:07.440
into the pilot's mind.

01:12:07.940 --> 01:12:09.060
Electromagnetic waves

01:12:09.060 --> 01:12:10.380
straight to the dome.

01:12:10.680 --> 01:12:12.000
This is the tamest part

01:12:12.000 --> 01:12:13.160
of Norseen's work.

01:12:14.040 --> 01:12:15.200
His theory describes

01:12:15.200 --> 01:12:16.180
systems that could

01:12:16.180 --> 01:12:17.000
push your brain

01:12:17.000 --> 01:12:18.740
into any target state.

01:12:18.960 --> 01:12:19.420
Aggression,

01:12:19.960 --> 01:12:20.340
calm,

01:12:20.920 --> 01:12:21.380
focus,

01:12:21.820 --> 01:12:22.380
ecstasy.

01:12:22.720 --> 01:12:23.400
I'm sure there are

01:12:23.400 --> 01:12:24.560
tons of implications

01:12:24.560 --> 01:12:25.480
for this work

01:12:25.480 --> 01:12:27.460
for CIA mind control programs

01:12:27.460 --> 01:12:28.600
like MKUltra,

01:12:29.020 --> 01:12:30.560
but let's stick to UFOs.

01:12:30.680 --> 01:12:32.040
According to his colleague,

01:12:32.220 --> 01:12:32.960
Duncan Lurie,

01:12:33.380 --> 01:12:34.440
Norseen theorized

01:12:34.440 --> 01:12:35.480
that every thought

01:12:35.480 --> 01:12:36.480
leaves an energy

01:12:36.480 --> 01:12:37.520
dispersion pattern.

01:12:37.840 --> 01:12:38.440
He called it

01:12:38.440 --> 01:12:39.320
a brain print,

01:12:39.640 --> 01:12:40.340
like a fingerprint,

01:12:40.340 --> 01:12:41.760
but for cognition.

01:12:42.480 --> 01:12:43.020
Intent,

01:12:43.760 --> 01:12:44.220
emotion,

01:12:44.920 --> 01:12:45.360
fear,

01:12:46.140 --> 01:12:46.480
joy.

01:12:46.880 --> 01:12:48.220
Each one has a pattern,

01:12:48.620 --> 01:12:50.000
not a static image,

01:12:50.380 --> 01:12:51.300
but something more

01:12:51.300 --> 01:12:52.100
like a posture,

01:12:52.360 --> 01:12:52.980
a configuration

01:12:52.980 --> 01:12:54.100
your brain holds

01:12:54.100 --> 01:12:54.780
that produces

01:12:54.780 --> 01:12:56.320
an action or state.

01:12:56.780 --> 01:12:57.420
So if thoughts

01:12:57.420 --> 01:12:58.400
or brain states

01:12:58.400 --> 01:12:59.340
leave patterns,

01:12:59.680 --> 01:13:00.580
how exactly

01:13:00.580 --> 01:13:01.640
do you capture them?

01:13:01.880 --> 01:13:03.120
As Norseen explained,

01:13:03.740 --> 01:13:04.580
think of your hand

01:13:04.580 --> 01:13:05.420
touching a mirror.

01:13:05.880 --> 01:13:07.000
It leaves a fingerprint.

01:13:07.540 --> 01:13:08.220
That's what

01:13:08.220 --> 01:13:09.500
biofusion does.

01:13:09.500 --> 01:13:11.460
It maps these brain prints

01:13:11.460 --> 01:13:13.080
using mathematical models.

01:13:13.460 --> 01:13:14.420
Just like you can find

01:13:14.420 --> 01:13:15.760
one person in a million

01:13:15.760 --> 01:13:16.680
through fingerprints,

01:13:16.980 --> 01:13:18.300
you can find one thought

01:13:18.300 --> 01:13:18.940
in a million.

01:13:19.860 --> 01:13:20.760
He wanted to build

01:13:20.760 --> 01:13:21.740
a full dictionary

01:13:21.740 --> 01:13:23.280
of these brain prints.

01:13:23.620 --> 01:13:24.460
The system learns

01:13:24.460 --> 01:13:25.680
what your brain looks like

01:13:25.680 --> 01:13:27.040
when you want to turn left,

01:13:27.360 --> 01:13:27.960
speed up,

01:13:28.340 --> 01:13:28.600
tilt,

01:13:28.760 --> 01:13:29.540
and stop.

01:13:29.760 --> 01:13:31.140
It doesn't just read you.

01:13:31.420 --> 01:13:32.220
It maps you.

01:13:32.640 --> 01:13:33.240
In theory,

01:13:33.420 --> 01:13:34.480
if you know the math

01:13:34.480 --> 01:13:35.480
of a brain pattern,

01:13:35.760 --> 01:13:37.000
you can potentially run it

01:13:37.000 --> 01:13:38.060
back into the brain

01:13:38.060 --> 01:13:39.440
and get the same state

01:13:39.440 --> 01:13:40.020
or feeling.

01:13:40.940 --> 01:13:42.560
You can think of biofusion

01:13:42.560 --> 01:13:44.360
like a brain-computer interface

01:13:44.360 --> 01:13:45.280
on steroids.

01:13:45.860 --> 01:13:46.460
Now here's where

01:13:46.460 --> 01:13:47.320
it gets interesting.

01:13:48.100 --> 01:13:49.120
A technical write-up

01:13:49.120 --> 01:13:50.800
by Autonomous019

01:13:50.800 --> 01:13:52.300
cites an internal

01:13:52.300 --> 01:13:54.300
Lockheed Martin R&D report

01:13:54.300 --> 01:13:55.660
by John Norseen

01:13:55.660 --> 01:13:56.260
called

01:13:56.260 --> 01:13:58.460
Biofusion Reflexive Control

01:13:58.460 --> 01:14:00.760
in Neuroergonomic Integration

01:14:00.760 --> 01:14:02.680
and Adaptive Cockpits.

01:14:06.400 --> 01:14:08.220
According to Norseen's citation,

01:14:08.560 --> 01:14:09.760
that report was funded

01:14:09.760 --> 01:14:10.980
under the contract

01:14:10.980 --> 01:14:13.260
N66001.

01:14:13.600 --> 01:14:14.280
I'll spare you

01:14:14.280 --> 01:14:15.140
the rest of the numbers.

01:14:15.440 --> 01:14:16.800
This is the same contract

01:14:16.800 --> 01:14:18.320
that NASA describes

01:14:18.320 --> 01:14:19.940
as an Aviation Weather

01:14:19.940 --> 01:14:21.640
Information Systems project.

01:14:22.100 --> 01:14:24.800
And that N66001 prefix

01:14:24.800 --> 01:14:26.400
traces back to the Navy's

01:14:26.400 --> 01:14:27.700
Space and Naval Warfare

01:14:27.700 --> 01:14:28.500
Systems Center

01:14:28.500 --> 01:14:29.380
in San Diego,

01:14:29.380 --> 01:14:30.460
today known as

01:14:30.460 --> 01:14:31.580
the Naval Information

01:14:31.580 --> 01:14:32.420
Warfare Center.

01:14:33.020 --> 01:14:33.660
So it appears

01:14:33.660 --> 01:14:35.420
we have a NASA-Navy hybrid

01:14:35.420 --> 01:14:36.460
and not too far

01:14:36.460 --> 01:14:37.200
from where the Nimitz

01:14:37.200 --> 01:14:38.080
Tic-Tac sighting

01:14:38.080 --> 01:14:39.540
occurred in 2004.

01:14:39.920 --> 01:14:40.680
Looked on a small

01:14:40.680 --> 01:14:42.100
saw-white Tic-Tac object

01:14:42.100 --> 01:14:43.300
with a longitudinal axis

01:14:43.300 --> 01:14:44.360
pointing north-south

01:14:44.360 --> 01:14:45.620
and moving very abruptly

01:14:45.620 --> 01:14:46.380
over the water.

01:14:46.500 --> 01:14:47.180
The same sighting

01:14:47.180 --> 01:14:48.040
that Ross Coulthart

01:14:48.040 --> 01:14:49.260
swears involved

01:14:49.260 --> 01:14:50.440
a Lockheed craft.

01:14:50.580 --> 01:14:52.400
I now know categorically

01:14:52.400 --> 01:14:53.760
that the Tic-Tac

01:14:53.760 --> 01:14:56.160
is Lockheed Martin technology.

01:14:56.420 --> 01:14:57.220
On the surface,

01:14:57.400 --> 01:14:58.420
John Norseen's work

01:14:58.420 --> 01:14:59.580
looks like it somehow

01:14:59.580 --> 01:15:00.920
made it into a NASA

01:15:00.920 --> 01:15:01.800
weather contract.

01:15:02.120 --> 01:15:02.920
But it lines up

01:15:02.920 --> 01:15:03.660
with a mirrored

01:15:03.660 --> 01:15:04.940
Lockheed Martin document

01:15:04.940 --> 01:15:06.120
from around 2000

01:15:06.120 --> 01:15:07.240
that lists his

01:15:07.240 --> 01:15:08.940
Biofusion R&D report

01:15:08.940 --> 01:15:10.880
with the same contract number.

01:15:11.320 --> 01:15:12.760
Multiple independent references

01:15:12.760 --> 01:15:14.480
all point to the same thing.

01:15:14.880 --> 01:15:16.120
Norseen's Biofusion

01:15:16.120 --> 01:15:17.220
Neurocockpit work

01:15:17.220 --> 01:15:19.160
was riding under that contract.

01:15:19.620 --> 01:15:21.020
I guess if you had a project

01:15:21.020 --> 01:15:23.140
that involves flying UFOs

01:15:23.140 --> 01:15:24.280
via mind control,

01:15:24.420 --> 01:15:25.180
it makes sense

01:15:25.180 --> 01:15:26.180
you might bury it

01:15:26.180 --> 01:15:27.740
inside a weather program.

01:15:27.740 --> 01:15:29.340
By the early 2000s,

01:15:29.420 --> 01:15:30.180
Norseen's work

01:15:30.180 --> 01:15:31.240
basically vanishes

01:15:31.240 --> 01:15:32.320
from public view.

01:15:32.960 --> 01:15:34.080
And not long after,

01:15:34.580 --> 01:15:35.540
he does too,

01:15:36.060 --> 01:15:38.220
under very strange circumstances.

01:15:38.860 --> 01:15:40.440
Shortly before a planned lecture

01:15:40.440 --> 01:15:41.880
at the Naval War College

01:15:41.880 --> 01:15:42.520
in Newport,

01:15:42.680 --> 01:15:43.860
he emailed colleagues

01:15:43.860 --> 01:15:44.900
a cryptic line

01:15:44.900 --> 01:15:46.320
about his future talk.

01:15:46.440 --> 01:15:48.320
He had sent me an email

01:15:48.320 --> 01:15:48.860
and said,

01:15:48.980 --> 01:15:50.080
and some of the other people

01:15:50.080 --> 01:15:50.700
from Ann's,

01:15:50.720 --> 01:15:51.040
and he said,

01:15:51.100 --> 01:15:51.280
listen,

01:15:51.400 --> 01:15:52.360
I'm giving a lecture

01:15:52.360 --> 01:15:54.000
on my latest research

01:15:54.000 --> 01:15:55.720
at the Naval College

01:15:55.720 --> 01:15:56.540
in Newport.

01:15:57.040 --> 01:15:59.100
Do you want a VIP pass

01:15:59.100 --> 01:16:00.580
to come and attend it?

01:16:00.640 --> 01:16:01.160
And I was like,

01:16:01.220 --> 01:16:01.940
oh yeah.

01:16:03.020 --> 01:16:03.840
So he said,

01:16:03.880 --> 01:16:04.100
okay,

01:16:04.140 --> 01:16:05.340
I'll get it all set up.

01:16:05.600 --> 01:16:06.680
And then at the end

01:16:06.680 --> 01:16:07.460
of his email,

01:16:08.220 --> 01:16:08.440
you know,

01:16:08.480 --> 01:16:09.280
he was into,

01:16:09.500 --> 01:16:10.700
I forget what the term

01:16:10.700 --> 01:16:11.940
is for this kind of

01:16:11.940 --> 01:16:13.980
use of language.

01:16:14.660 --> 01:16:15.060
Semiotics.

01:16:15.280 --> 01:16:16.120
Semiotics, yeah.

01:16:16.120 --> 01:16:17.860
He was really into that.

01:16:18.340 --> 01:16:20.480
And at the last sentence

01:16:20.480 --> 01:16:22.020
in his email said,

01:16:23.240 --> 01:16:24.020
Nor,

01:16:24.380 --> 01:16:26.540
he said,

01:16:26.680 --> 01:16:29.420
I RV'd the upcoming

01:16:29.420 --> 01:16:32.840
lecture,

01:16:33.620 --> 01:16:35.880
John not heard

01:16:35.880 --> 01:16:37.320
nor seen.

01:16:38.420 --> 01:16:39.020
Whoa.

01:16:39.500 --> 01:16:41.500
And I remember calling Ann

01:16:41.500 --> 01:16:41.980
and saying,

01:16:42.100 --> 01:16:42.620
hey Ann,

01:16:42.760 --> 01:16:43.680
what the heck

01:16:43.680 --> 01:16:45.240
does this last sentence mean?

01:16:45.240 --> 01:16:46.660
John not heard nor seen.

01:16:46.760 --> 01:16:47.340
I know he's in the

01:16:47.340 --> 01:16:48.260
semiotics and stuff,

01:16:48.360 --> 01:16:48.840
so, you know,

01:16:48.920 --> 01:16:50.180
not nor seen

01:16:50.180 --> 01:16:51.320
is his last name,

01:16:51.420 --> 01:16:53.040
but John not heard

01:16:53.040 --> 01:16:53.760
nor seen.

01:16:54.180 --> 01:16:55.480
And then just like

01:16:55.480 --> 01:16:56.620
two weeks after that,

01:16:57.080 --> 01:16:57.960
he was found dead

01:16:57.960 --> 01:16:58.900
in a motel room.

01:16:59.140 --> 01:17:00.180
Jesus Christ.

01:17:00.280 --> 01:17:01.020
So that was some sort

01:17:01.020 --> 01:17:02.300
of code where it's like

01:17:02.300 --> 01:17:03.380
he remote viewed

01:17:03.380 --> 01:17:04.200
his own death.

01:17:04.200 --> 01:17:04.460
He remote viewed it

01:17:04.460 --> 01:17:05.500
and he wasn't there.

01:17:05.640 --> 01:17:06.480
And this was code

01:17:06.480 --> 01:17:07.780
to say he's not heard

01:17:07.780 --> 01:17:08.600
nor seen.

01:17:08.740 --> 01:17:08.820
Yeah.

01:17:08.900 --> 01:17:09.020
I mean,

01:17:09.020 --> 01:17:10.000
what else could that mean?

01:17:10.460 --> 01:17:11.780
Oh my God.

01:17:12.160 --> 01:17:13.200
Nor seen was gone,

01:17:13.200 --> 01:17:14.440
but the kind of work

01:17:14.440 --> 01:17:15.640
he was doing wasn't.

01:17:15.820 --> 01:17:17.260
And roughly 20 years later,

01:17:17.620 --> 01:17:18.500
they resurface,

01:17:18.780 --> 01:17:19.920
but in a different form.

01:17:20.220 --> 01:17:21.180
Enter Lockheed Martin

01:17:21.180 --> 01:17:22.800
engineers Charles Chase

01:17:22.800 --> 01:17:23.880
and Gerald Jonas

01:17:23.880 --> 01:17:25.560
with a patent called

01:17:25.560 --> 01:17:26.920
Cognitive Enhancement

01:17:26.920 --> 01:17:27.880
Using Feedback.

01:17:28.140 --> 01:17:28.900
I've personally had

01:17:28.900 --> 01:17:29.840
the pleasure of meeting

01:17:29.840 --> 01:17:30.580
Charles Chase

01:17:30.580 --> 01:17:31.900
and think he's a genius.

01:17:32.260 --> 01:17:32.880
And this patent

01:17:32.880 --> 01:17:33.840
might sound boring

01:17:33.840 --> 01:17:34.720
on the face of it,

01:17:34.800 --> 01:17:35.500
but it's not.

01:17:35.720 --> 01:17:36.460
It's describing

01:17:36.460 --> 01:17:37.780
a closed loop system

01:17:37.780 --> 01:17:39.360
that reads your brain waves,

01:17:39.660 --> 01:17:40.220
compares them

01:17:40.220 --> 01:17:41.620
to a target brain state,

01:17:41.620 --> 01:17:42.820
and then hits you

01:17:42.820 --> 01:17:43.420
with light,

01:17:43.780 --> 01:17:44.120
sound,

01:17:44.240 --> 01:17:45.640
or electromagnetic pulses

01:17:45.640 --> 01:17:46.960
until your brain

01:17:46.960 --> 01:17:47.680
is nudged

01:17:47.680 --> 01:17:48.820
towards that target,

01:17:49.020 --> 01:17:49.940
like a tuning fork

01:17:49.940 --> 01:17:51.000
for the human mind.

01:17:51.120 --> 01:17:51.700
It's essentially

01:17:51.700 --> 01:17:53.180
an extremely sophisticated

01:17:53.180 --> 01:17:55.140
version of biofeedback.

01:17:56.720 --> 01:17:58.020
I've asked Charles Chase

01:17:58.020 --> 01:17:58.900
and he doesn't know

01:17:58.900 --> 01:17:59.400
nor seen,

01:17:59.540 --> 01:18:00.380
but you have to admit

01:18:00.380 --> 01:18:01.580
it is pretty interesting

01:18:01.580 --> 01:18:03.040
that there is a lineage

01:18:03.040 --> 01:18:04.780
pointing to the same company

01:18:04.780 --> 01:18:05.800
and the same sort

01:18:05.800 --> 01:18:06.560
of control loop.

01:18:06.840 --> 01:18:07.580
Measure your brain,

01:18:07.580 --> 01:18:09.140
compare it to a target state,

01:18:09.620 --> 01:18:10.380
stimulate it,

01:18:10.380 --> 01:18:11.360
and remeasure it.

01:18:11.880 --> 01:18:12.420
And then there are

01:18:12.420 --> 01:18:13.780
other people at this company

01:18:13.780 --> 01:18:15.260
up to the executive level

01:18:15.260 --> 01:18:16.460
that are talking about

01:18:16.460 --> 01:18:18.160
flying UFOs with your mind.

01:18:18.620 --> 01:18:19.400
So it looks like

01:18:19.400 --> 01:18:21.540
Norseen's adaptive cockpit ideas

01:18:21.540 --> 01:18:22.700
could be the prototype.

01:18:23.360 --> 01:18:24.820
Looks like the weather project

01:18:24.820 --> 01:18:25.760
grew some teeth.

01:18:26.200 --> 01:18:27.200
In multiple interviews,

01:18:27.400 --> 01:18:28.340
including with me,

01:18:28.640 --> 01:18:30.680
the consciousness is activated

01:18:30.680 --> 01:18:31.900
through heightening intuition

01:18:31.900 --> 01:18:32.840
and lowering intellect.

01:18:33.200 --> 01:18:34.120
Barber describes

01:18:34.120 --> 01:18:35.900
consciousness craft interfaces

01:18:35.900 --> 01:18:37.220
that sound impossible.

01:18:37.220 --> 01:18:39.280
But here's the documented R&D

01:18:39.280 --> 01:18:40.500
showing this technology

01:18:40.500 --> 01:18:42.000
has been actively developed.

01:18:42.280 --> 01:18:43.500
Whether it's been successfully

01:18:43.500 --> 01:18:44.780
integrated with exotic

01:18:44.780 --> 01:18:45.780
propulsion systems,

01:18:46.100 --> 01:18:47.520
we don't ultimately know.

01:18:47.700 --> 01:18:49.180
But the technical capability

01:18:49.180 --> 01:18:50.180
Barber described

01:18:50.180 --> 01:18:52.260
isn't necessarily science fiction.

01:18:52.540 --> 01:18:53.860
It's just Lockheed Martin,

01:18:54.300 --> 01:18:55.300
circa 1999.

01:18:56.640 --> 01:18:57.700
And by 2018,

01:18:58.200 --> 01:18:59.720
that same basic dream

01:18:59.720 --> 01:19:01.120
of humans interfacing

01:19:01.120 --> 01:19:02.540
directly with machines

01:19:02.540 --> 01:19:03.860
was no longer buried

01:19:03.860 --> 01:19:05.680
in obscure papers or patents.

01:19:05.680 --> 01:19:07.140
That year, DARPA launched

01:19:07.140 --> 01:19:08.800
a program called N3,

01:19:09.060 --> 01:19:11.060
Next Generation Non-Surgical

01:19:11.060 --> 01:19:12.440
Neurotechnology.

01:19:12.700 --> 01:19:14.400
DARPA's official program brief

01:19:14.400 --> 01:19:15.760
openly talks about

01:19:15.760 --> 01:19:17.100
building bi-directional

01:19:17.100 --> 01:19:18.780
brain-machine interfaces

01:19:18.780 --> 01:19:20.140
for military use,

01:19:20.280 --> 01:19:21.740
including for things like

01:19:21.740 --> 01:19:23.200
control of unmanned

01:19:23.200 --> 01:19:24.140
aerial vehicles.

01:19:24.360 --> 01:19:25.000
One of the teams

01:19:25.000 --> 01:19:26.620
that advanced in N3

01:19:26.620 --> 01:19:28.080
was led by Battelle.

01:19:28.400 --> 01:19:29.040
And if you've done

01:19:29.040 --> 01:19:30.180
any deep research

01:19:30.180 --> 01:19:31.900
on UFO legacy programs,

01:19:32.220 --> 01:19:33.120
you know that

01:19:33.120 --> 01:19:34.620
Battelle Memorial Institute

01:19:34.620 --> 01:19:36.180
is all over it.

01:19:36.300 --> 01:19:37.240
According to Battelle's

01:19:37.240 --> 01:19:38.960
own 2020 press release,

01:19:39.160 --> 01:19:40.060
their team progressed

01:19:40.060 --> 01:19:41.680
to phase two of the program.

01:19:42.000 --> 01:19:43.020
They were working directly

01:19:43.020 --> 01:19:44.640
with the Air Force Research Lab,

01:19:44.800 --> 01:19:45.540
Carnegie Mellon,

01:19:45.620 --> 01:19:47.080
and others on a system

01:19:47.080 --> 01:19:48.400
called BRAINSTORMS,

01:19:48.720 --> 01:19:49.600
which stands for

01:19:49.600 --> 01:19:51.240
Brain System to Transmit

01:19:51.240 --> 01:19:52.060
or Receive

01:19:52.060 --> 01:19:54.020
Magneto-Electric Signals.

01:19:54.260 --> 01:19:54.860
BRAINSTORMS

01:19:54.860 --> 01:19:56.740
uses nanoscale devices

01:19:56.740 --> 01:19:59.020
injected into the human bloodstream

01:19:59.020 --> 01:20:00.880
and guided with magnets

01:20:00.880 --> 01:20:03.040
into specific areas of the brain

01:20:03.040 --> 01:20:04.700
as part of a system designed

01:20:04.700 --> 01:20:07.220
for bi-directional neural interfacing.

01:20:07.380 --> 01:20:08.240
So by 2020,

01:20:08.420 --> 01:20:10.120
you don't just have vague patents

01:20:10.120 --> 01:20:11.180
and R&D rumors.

01:20:11.420 --> 01:20:13.360
You have DARPA openly funding

01:20:13.360 --> 01:20:15.120
a nanoscale injectable

01:20:15.120 --> 01:20:16.420
brain-computer interface

01:20:16.420 --> 01:20:18.660
with the Air Force Research Lab's

01:20:18.660 --> 01:20:19.100
involvement

01:20:19.100 --> 01:20:20.800
that could be a stepping stone

01:20:20.800 --> 01:20:21.940
towards warfighters

01:20:21.940 --> 01:20:23.260
eventually interfacing

01:20:23.260 --> 01:20:24.360
with aerial vehicles.

01:20:24.560 --> 01:20:26.100
Or it could simply represent

01:20:26.100 --> 01:20:26.900
an advancement

01:20:26.900 --> 01:20:28.020
in that capability,

01:20:28.280 --> 01:20:29.200
which was established

01:20:29.200 --> 01:20:30.320
years before.

01:20:30.320 --> 01:20:33.580
Now for a different track.

01:20:33.880 --> 01:20:34.720
Stay with me here.

01:20:35.580 --> 01:20:36.440
In 2016,

01:20:36.840 --> 01:20:38.180
the Navy filed a patent

01:20:38.180 --> 01:20:39.100
under inventor

01:20:39.100 --> 01:20:40.120
Salvatore Pais

01:20:40.120 --> 01:20:41.540
for what they called

01:20:41.540 --> 01:20:43.100
craft using an inertial

01:20:43.100 --> 01:20:44.420
mass reduction device.

01:20:44.660 --> 01:20:46.560
The patent describes a craft

01:20:46.560 --> 01:20:47.500
that manipulates

01:20:47.500 --> 01:20:49.600
high-energy electromagnetic fields

01:20:49.600 --> 01:20:51.340
to achieve exotic propulsion,

01:20:51.640 --> 01:20:52.800
a setup that requires

01:20:52.800 --> 01:20:54.580
precise, real-time control

01:20:54.580 --> 01:20:56.100
of its own field geometry.

01:20:56.440 --> 01:20:57.280
You need something

01:20:57.280 --> 01:20:58.060
that can sense

01:20:58.060 --> 01:20:59.660
its internal field configuration,

01:20:59.660 --> 01:21:01.300
and how it interacts

01:21:01.300 --> 01:21:02.620
with the surrounding environment

01:21:02.620 --> 01:21:04.740
and adjust in real time.

01:21:04.980 --> 01:21:05.700
Something faster

01:21:05.700 --> 01:21:06.460
than a joystick.

01:21:06.800 --> 01:21:07.840
Faster than a keyboard.

01:21:08.240 --> 01:21:09.420
Something like a mind.

01:21:09.580 --> 01:21:10.420
What you won't see

01:21:10.420 --> 01:21:11.300
in the open record

01:21:11.300 --> 01:21:12.920
is the obvious next step.

01:21:13.060 --> 01:21:14.560
Plug those worlds together.

01:21:14.880 --> 01:21:16.220
If Jake Barber is right,

01:21:16.640 --> 01:21:17.560
that missing link

01:21:17.560 --> 01:21:19.660
lives in special access programs

01:21:19.660 --> 01:21:21.840
that don't get patented at all.

01:21:21.980 --> 01:21:22.920
So to recap,

01:21:23.160 --> 01:21:23.740
Layer 1.

01:21:24.400 --> 01:21:25.340
Lockheed develops

01:21:25.340 --> 01:21:26.080
and patents

01:21:26.080 --> 01:21:27.760
brain-to-machine interfaces.

01:21:27.760 --> 01:21:28.760
Layer 2.

01:21:29.120 --> 01:21:30.400
The Navy patents craft

01:21:30.400 --> 01:21:31.180
that require

01:21:31.180 --> 01:21:33.040
electromagnetic field manipulation.

01:21:33.580 --> 01:21:34.280
Layer 3.

01:21:34.780 --> 01:21:35.820
Psionic assets.

01:21:36.260 --> 01:21:37.340
Human intuitives

01:21:37.340 --> 01:21:39.240
jacked into exotic craft

01:21:39.240 --> 01:21:40.620
through neural interfaces,

01:21:41.180 --> 01:21:42.240
translating thought

01:21:42.240 --> 01:21:43.300
into propulsion.

01:21:43.660 --> 01:21:44.380
I'm not saying

01:21:44.380 --> 01:21:45.520
that we have a verified

01:21:45.520 --> 01:21:47.120
Salvatore Pais saucer

01:21:47.120 --> 01:21:47.800
in a hangar

01:21:47.800 --> 01:21:49.640
synced to a psionic asset

01:21:49.640 --> 01:21:51.080
with that exact setup.

01:21:51.460 --> 01:21:52.260
I am saying

01:21:52.260 --> 01:21:54.160
that Barber's psionic pilot story

01:21:54.160 --> 01:21:55.180
sounds wild.

01:21:55.180 --> 01:21:57.560
Until you look at the R&D lineage

01:21:57.560 --> 01:21:58.300
and realize

01:21:58.300 --> 01:21:59.940
every piece of that stack

01:21:59.940 --> 01:22:01.260
is already sitting

01:22:01.260 --> 01:22:02.180
in white papers,

01:22:02.420 --> 01:22:02.800
patents,

01:22:03.220 --> 01:22:04.340
and weather contracts.

01:22:05.860 --> 01:22:06.700
So far,

01:22:06.800 --> 01:22:07.820
we have a fake mountain,

01:22:08.300 --> 01:22:09.360
drugged psychics,

01:22:09.840 --> 01:22:10.760
and spacecrafts

01:22:10.760 --> 01:22:11.560
that only fly

01:22:11.560 --> 01:22:12.240
if you plug

01:22:12.240 --> 01:22:13.540
a human mind into them.

01:22:13.820 --> 01:22:14.360
What's next,

01:22:14.440 --> 01:22:14.880
do you ask?

01:22:14.960 --> 01:22:15.780
The moon's fake,

01:22:16.140 --> 01:22:17.300
clouds aren't really clouds,

01:22:17.720 --> 01:22:18.980
birds are surveilling us?

01:22:19.200 --> 01:22:19.560
Yeah,

01:22:19.920 --> 01:22:21.240
DARPA's R&D portfolio

01:22:21.240 --> 01:22:22.280
does not make that

01:22:22.280 --> 01:22:22.920
less creepy.

01:22:22.920 --> 01:22:24.460
Zoom out of Koyame

01:22:24.460 --> 01:22:25.740
and you'll see a pattern.

01:22:26.260 --> 01:22:26.640
Mountains,

01:22:27.160 --> 01:22:28.080
paramilitaries,

01:22:28.260 --> 01:22:29.280
and vanishing crafts.

01:22:30.060 --> 01:22:31.180
It starts to look

01:22:31.180 --> 01:22:32.200
less like random

01:22:32.200 --> 01:22:33.240
campfire stories

01:22:33.240 --> 01:22:34.920
and more like puzzle pieces.

01:22:35.200 --> 01:22:35.900
Take Sedona,

01:22:36.220 --> 01:22:37.240
Vision Quest capital

01:22:37.240 --> 01:22:37.860
of America,

01:22:38.400 --> 01:22:39.480
the land of crystals

01:22:39.480 --> 01:22:41.020
and trust fund shamans.

01:22:41.420 --> 01:22:42.160
Famed for its

01:22:42.160 --> 01:22:43.100
Martian landscape

01:22:43.100 --> 01:22:44.300
and vortex spas,

01:22:44.560 --> 01:22:45.300
it's all very

01:22:45.300 --> 01:22:45.560
eat,

01:22:45.640 --> 01:22:45.760
pray,

01:22:45.860 --> 01:22:46.200
love.

01:22:46.340 --> 01:22:47.260
But once the sun

01:22:47.260 --> 01:22:48.920
sets behind the red rocks,

01:22:49.300 --> 01:22:50.760
the vibe starts to shift.

01:22:50.760 --> 01:22:53.020
The notorious Bradshaw Ranch

01:22:53.020 --> 01:22:54.200
is ground zero

01:22:54.200 --> 01:22:55.180
for Sedona's

01:22:55.180 --> 01:22:56.120
high strangeness.

01:22:56.380 --> 01:22:57.020
There's even a book

01:22:57.020 --> 01:22:57.680
about it called

01:22:57.680 --> 01:22:58.800
Merging Dimensions

01:22:58.800 --> 01:22:59.960
involving a rumored

01:22:59.960 --> 01:23:01.240
portal on the ranch,

01:23:01.820 --> 01:23:03.120
massive cargo planes

01:23:03.120 --> 01:23:04.520
descending towards mountains

01:23:04.520 --> 01:23:05.920
where nothing exists,

01:23:06.500 --> 01:23:07.440
and lights shooting

01:23:07.440 --> 01:23:08.260
out of canyons

01:23:08.260 --> 01:23:09.340
as if the landscape

01:23:09.340 --> 01:23:10.700
itself is alive.

01:23:11.200 --> 01:23:12.620
There are constant claims

01:23:12.620 --> 01:23:13.820
of strange activity

01:23:13.820 --> 01:23:15.100
at Bradshaw Ranch

01:23:15.100 --> 01:23:16.120
in Secret Canyon

01:23:16.120 --> 01:23:17.760
with reports of guys

01:23:17.760 --> 01:23:19.500
with military-style guns.

01:23:19.500 --> 01:23:20.420
No surprise,

01:23:20.620 --> 01:23:21.420
the ranch was sold

01:23:21.420 --> 01:23:22.960
to the U.S. National Forest

01:23:22.960 --> 01:23:24.440
for climate research

01:23:24.440 --> 01:23:25.440
in partnership

01:23:25.440 --> 01:23:27.480
with the Department of Energy

01:23:27.480 --> 01:23:29.960
and Oak Ridge National Lab.

01:23:30.160 --> 01:23:31.060
Nothing to see here.

01:23:31.300 --> 01:23:32.820
Whispers of a rumored base

01:23:32.820 --> 01:23:33.760
near Secret Mountain

01:23:33.760 --> 01:23:34.560
aren't new.

01:23:35.280 --> 01:23:36.500
Journalist Ross Colthart

01:23:36.500 --> 01:23:37.540
went to Sedona

01:23:37.540 --> 01:23:39.180
and came back a believer.

01:23:39.320 --> 01:23:40.280
I am in no doubt

01:23:40.280 --> 01:23:41.400
whatsoever, Jesse,

01:23:41.780 --> 01:23:42.760
that there is a deep

01:23:42.760 --> 01:23:44.640
underground military bunker

01:23:44.640 --> 01:23:45.260
that was built

01:23:45.260 --> 01:23:46.520
in the 1950s

01:23:46.520 --> 01:23:48.340
under Secret Mountain.

01:23:48.340 --> 01:23:49.480
That's what it's called.

01:23:49.780 --> 01:23:50.960
It's the hilarious thing.

01:23:51.000 --> 01:23:51.960
It's named Secret Mountain.

01:23:51.960 --> 01:23:53.500
It's called Secret Mountain.

01:23:53.640 --> 01:23:54.040
Unbelievable.

01:23:54.480 --> 01:23:55.320
And that's not all.

01:23:55.700 --> 01:23:56.600
Outside of consulting

01:23:56.600 --> 01:23:58.100
multiple on-site witnesses,

01:23:58.700 --> 01:24:00.220
Ross personally witnessed

01:24:00.220 --> 01:24:01.380
anomalous activity

01:24:01.380 --> 01:24:02.540
around Secret Mountain.

01:24:03.020 --> 01:24:03.820
And if you looked

01:24:03.820 --> 01:24:04.780
at a particular place

01:24:04.780 --> 01:24:05.640
over Secret Mountain,

01:24:06.220 --> 01:24:07.020
you would see

01:24:07.020 --> 01:24:09.200
this big orb

01:24:09.200 --> 01:24:10.480
being escorted

01:24:10.480 --> 01:24:11.280
by helicopters

01:24:11.280 --> 01:24:12.860
rising from behind

01:24:12.860 --> 01:24:13.480
Secret Mountain.

01:24:13.480 --> 01:24:14.600
and we watched

01:24:14.600 --> 01:24:16.000
at 1.30 in the morning

01:24:16.000 --> 01:24:16.940
and sure enough,

01:24:17.520 --> 01:24:20.020
up comes this beautiful

01:24:20.020 --> 01:24:21.040
golden orb.

01:24:21.420 --> 01:24:21.980
Gigantic.

01:24:22.440 --> 01:24:23.300
It's not every day

01:24:23.300 --> 01:24:24.640
you see orbs escorted

01:24:24.640 --> 01:24:25.600
by Blackhawks

01:24:25.600 --> 01:24:27.220
like a presidential motorcade.

01:24:27.340 --> 01:24:28.280
But zoom in a little

01:24:28.280 --> 01:24:29.300
and look closely.

01:24:29.720 --> 01:24:31.000
You'll find something else.

01:24:31.660 --> 01:24:32.740
Investigators digging

01:24:32.740 --> 01:24:33.540
into rumors

01:24:33.540 --> 01:24:34.980
of underground facilities

01:24:34.980 --> 01:24:36.180
near Secret Mountain

01:24:36.180 --> 01:24:37.420
and Bradshaw Ranch

01:24:37.420 --> 01:24:38.500
kept hitting

01:24:38.500 --> 01:24:39.560
the same anomaly.

01:24:39.560 --> 01:24:40.760
A tunnel,

01:24:41.220 --> 01:24:42.420
geophysical surveys

01:24:42.420 --> 01:24:43.680
and magnetometry

01:24:43.680 --> 01:24:45.400
by Terra Exploration Group

01:24:45.400 --> 01:24:46.700
showed a straight,

01:24:47.040 --> 01:24:47.900
man-made tunnel

01:24:47.900 --> 01:24:49.360
roughly 50 feet

01:24:49.360 --> 01:24:50.060
in diameter

01:24:50.060 --> 01:24:51.220
running like

01:24:51.220 --> 01:24:52.160
a hidden artery

01:24:52.160 --> 01:24:53.560
from Secret Mountain

01:24:53.560 --> 01:24:55.040
to Bradshaw Ranch

01:24:55.040 --> 01:24:56.240
to the front gate

01:24:56.240 --> 01:24:57.300
of the Clarkdale

01:24:57.300 --> 01:24:58.120
Cement Plant,

01:24:58.500 --> 01:24:59.640
which John Bradshaw

01:24:59.640 --> 01:25:01.080
claims used to be

01:25:01.080 --> 01:25:02.180
the biggest employer

01:25:02.180 --> 01:25:02.840
in town

01:25:02.840 --> 01:25:04.000
and was guarded

01:25:04.000 --> 01:25:04.900
and fenced

01:25:04.900 --> 01:25:06.240
like a military site.

01:25:06.660 --> 01:25:07.840
And there's

01:25:07.840 --> 01:25:09.320
massive amounts

01:25:09.320 --> 01:25:10.340
of electrical power

01:25:10.340 --> 01:25:11.460
going into

01:25:11.460 --> 01:25:12.600
the ground

01:25:12.600 --> 01:25:13.900
under Bradshaw Ranch.

01:25:14.620 --> 01:25:17.220
And we didn't put this

01:25:17.220 --> 01:25:19.720
in the feature-length film

01:25:19.720 --> 01:25:20.500
that we put to air

01:25:20.500 --> 01:25:21.160
on Primetime,

01:25:21.260 --> 01:25:21.800
but it runs

01:25:21.800 --> 01:25:22.920
in the full-length interview

01:25:22.920 --> 01:25:23.760
with Paul,

01:25:23.880 --> 01:25:24.300
my friend.

01:25:25.340 --> 01:25:27.220
He did a ground-penetrating

01:25:27.220 --> 01:25:28.320
radar check

01:25:28.320 --> 01:25:29.760
on the road

01:25:29.760 --> 01:25:31.060
around Bradshaw Ranch

01:25:31.060 --> 01:25:32.500
and we found

01:25:32.500 --> 01:25:33.840
a 50-foot-wide

01:25:33.840 --> 01:25:35.860
reinforced steel concrete

01:25:35.860 --> 01:25:36.940
highly visible

01:25:36.940 --> 01:25:38.400
on ground-penetrating radar.

01:25:38.400 --> 01:25:39.860
Literally just under

01:25:39.860 --> 01:25:40.220
the ground.

01:25:40.480 --> 01:25:40.860
Whoa.

01:25:41.360 --> 01:25:42.160
If you think this is

01:25:42.160 --> 01:25:42.860
beyond belief,

01:25:43.080 --> 01:25:44.220
underground military bases

01:25:44.220 --> 01:25:46.240
exist across the United States.

01:25:46.660 --> 01:25:47.640
They are called DUMs

01:25:47.640 --> 01:25:48.680
or Deep Underground

01:25:48.680 --> 01:25:49.640
Military Bases.

01:25:50.120 --> 01:25:50.840
Richard Sauter

01:25:50.840 --> 01:25:51.760
wrote an amazing book

01:25:51.760 --> 01:25:52.260
about them

01:25:52.260 --> 01:25:52.940
that I recommend

01:25:52.940 --> 01:25:53.700
you check out.

01:25:54.140 --> 01:25:55.320
There are also reports

01:25:55.320 --> 01:25:56.680
of hikers near Sedona

01:25:56.680 --> 01:25:57.940
walking into something

01:25:57.940 --> 01:25:59.780
out of a black op fever dream.

01:25:59.780 --> 01:26:01.580
Armed Men in Black,

01:26:02.000 --> 01:26:03.540
Insignia-free uniforms,

01:26:04.060 --> 01:26:05.560
M16s in hand,

01:26:05.840 --> 01:26:06.840
standing in the middle

01:26:06.840 --> 01:26:08.660
of Coconino National Forest.

01:26:09.120 --> 01:26:10.340
These guys aren't militia.

01:26:10.520 --> 01:26:11.840
They don't match any unit

01:26:11.840 --> 01:26:12.960
anyone can identify.

01:26:13.240 --> 01:26:14.680
And this isn't just Sedona.

01:26:15.080 --> 01:26:17.140
This exact same ghost force

01:26:17.140 --> 01:26:18.240
keeps popping up

01:26:18.240 --> 01:26:19.420
in other hot zones

01:26:19.420 --> 01:26:21.240
across the United States.

01:26:21.620 --> 01:26:22.660
Head northeast

01:26:22.660 --> 01:26:23.780
to Skinwalker Ranch

01:26:23.780 --> 01:26:25.200
in Utah's Uinta Basin,

01:26:25.200 --> 01:26:26.260
and the vibe shifts

01:26:26.260 --> 01:26:27.200
from moonstones

01:26:27.200 --> 01:26:28.120
to pure dread.

01:26:28.520 --> 01:26:29.520
This place doesn't

01:26:29.520 --> 01:26:30.140
want you here.

01:26:30.360 --> 01:26:31.180
The Ute tribe

01:26:31.180 --> 01:26:32.480
won't even talk about it.

01:26:32.560 --> 01:26:33.140
They call it

01:26:33.140 --> 01:26:33.920
Cursed Ground,

01:26:34.160 --> 01:26:35.340
the path of the Skinwalker.

01:26:35.680 --> 01:26:36.380
And if you spend

01:26:36.380 --> 01:26:37.860
any time on the ranch,

01:26:38.060 --> 01:26:39.620
you start to understand why.

01:26:39.860 --> 01:26:40.760
Drones malfunction,

01:26:41.300 --> 01:26:42.620
helicopters lose power,

01:26:43.040 --> 01:26:44.000
equipment dies.

01:26:44.160 --> 01:26:45.480
I am transfixed on

01:26:45.480 --> 01:26:47.160
that tacky room.

01:26:48.120 --> 01:26:49.120
For all intents and purposes,

01:26:49.360 --> 01:26:50.720
I'm in that room.

01:26:51.020 --> 01:26:52.680
And so I just,

01:26:52.780 --> 01:26:54.560
I said out loud,

01:26:54.560 --> 01:26:55.420
okay, this is stupid.

01:26:56.080 --> 01:26:56.980
And then I said,

01:26:57.860 --> 01:26:58.240
all right,

01:26:58.460 --> 01:26:59.600
if you got something

01:26:59.600 --> 01:27:00.420
you want to show me,

01:27:00.480 --> 01:27:00.840
show me.

01:27:01.260 --> 01:27:01.720
If you got something

01:27:01.720 --> 01:27:02.360
you want to tell me,

01:27:02.600 --> 01:27:02.920
tell me.

01:27:02.920 --> 01:27:03.560
What the hell?

01:27:03.760 --> 01:27:04.460
I live in?

01:27:04.780 --> 01:27:05.800
That's creepy.

01:27:07.400 --> 01:27:08.440
UFOs don't just

01:27:08.440 --> 01:27:09.580
fly over Skinwalker.

01:27:09.980 --> 01:27:11.560
They interact and descend,

01:27:11.940 --> 01:27:13.100
vanishing into mesas

01:27:13.100 --> 01:27:13.920
like ghosts

01:27:13.920 --> 01:27:15.200
passing through walls.

01:27:15.520 --> 01:27:16.120
Sound familiar?

01:27:17.020 --> 01:27:18.080
Owner Brandon Fugel

01:27:18.080 --> 01:27:19.200
openly describes

01:27:19.200 --> 01:27:20.400
Blackhawks circling

01:27:20.400 --> 01:27:21.580
with no transponders,

01:27:21.920 --> 01:27:22.760
shaking the house,

01:27:23.060 --> 01:27:24.540
running constant surveillance

01:27:24.540 --> 01:27:26.540
We had a situation

01:27:26.540 --> 01:27:27.340
above the triangle

01:27:27.340 --> 01:27:27.900
where we were

01:27:27.900 --> 01:27:28.760
launching rockets,

01:27:28.880 --> 01:27:29.280
of course,

01:27:29.380 --> 01:27:31.240
one of numerous occasions.

01:27:32.160 --> 01:27:34.240
And the prominent

01:27:34.240 --> 01:27:35.200
UAP,

01:27:36.060 --> 01:27:37.460
Unidentified Aerial Phenomena,

01:27:37.640 --> 01:27:39.520
ends up appearing.

01:27:39.820 --> 01:27:40.800
And then what happens

01:27:40.800 --> 01:27:42.880
within minutes following,

01:27:44.060 --> 01:27:45.340
the Blackhawk helicopter

01:27:45.340 --> 01:27:48.080
comes right over the mesa,

01:27:48.320 --> 01:27:49.480
descends over the property,

01:27:49.600 --> 01:27:50.760
and just hovers

01:27:50.760 --> 01:27:53.280
right over the south field.

01:27:53.280 --> 01:27:55.340
He also described a time

01:27:55.340 --> 01:27:56.460
where a UFO dropped

01:27:56.460 --> 01:27:57.560
down from the sky,

01:27:58.120 --> 01:27:59.680
entered the east field portion

01:27:59.680 --> 01:28:01.420
of the ranch below a helicopter,

01:28:01.860 --> 01:28:03.740
and then exited from a mesa.

01:28:04.180 --> 01:28:05.320
Does it look like it comes

01:28:05.320 --> 01:28:05.900
from right there?

01:28:05.900 --> 01:28:07.300
It came out of the mesa,

01:28:07.400 --> 01:28:08.140
right there.

01:28:09.140 --> 01:28:09.680
Wow.

01:28:10.680 --> 01:28:12.680
That is unbelievable, gentlemen.

01:28:13.440 --> 01:28:14.360
During all of this,

01:28:14.540 --> 01:28:16.360
drones and other sensor equipment

01:28:16.360 --> 01:28:17.280
malfunctioned.

01:28:17.520 --> 01:28:19.320
Previous Skinwalker Ranch owner,

01:28:19.440 --> 01:28:20.240
Robert Bigelow,

01:28:20.240 --> 01:28:21.660
tells another story

01:28:21.660 --> 01:28:23.140
about a UFO flying

01:28:23.140 --> 01:28:24.300
lazy figure eights

01:28:24.300 --> 01:28:25.100
at low altitude,

01:28:25.360 --> 01:28:26.480
then shooting straight

01:28:26.480 --> 01:28:27.200
into a mountain.

01:28:27.560 --> 01:28:28.560
And so they stand there

01:28:28.560 --> 01:28:29.460
and they're watching this,

01:28:29.920 --> 01:28:31.020
and then it deviates

01:28:31.020 --> 01:28:31.960
dramatically,

01:28:32.380 --> 01:28:33.380
and it shoots off

01:28:33.380 --> 01:28:34.120
at low altitude

01:28:34.120 --> 01:28:36.180
right into the mountain itself.

01:28:36.860 --> 01:28:38.140
But there's no explosion.

01:28:38.860 --> 01:28:39.580
It's just gone.

01:28:39.840 --> 01:28:40.660
In another case

01:28:40.660 --> 01:28:41.780
near Skinwalker Ranch,

01:28:41.980 --> 01:28:43.560
he describes a similar craft

01:28:43.560 --> 01:28:44.740
doing the same thing,

01:28:44.940 --> 01:28:46.440
shooting straight into the mountain

01:28:46.440 --> 01:28:47.460
as if the stone

01:28:47.460 --> 01:28:48.160
was a doorway.

01:28:49.720 --> 01:28:50.680
If we zoom out,

01:28:50.780 --> 01:28:52.140
it gets even stranger.

01:28:52.760 --> 01:28:53.880
During the CIA's

01:28:53.880 --> 01:28:54.980
remote viewing program

01:28:54.980 --> 01:28:56.160
in 1973,

01:28:56.880 --> 01:28:58.440
psychic spy Pat Price

01:28:58.440 --> 01:28:59.780
described a massive

01:28:59.780 --> 01:29:00.920
underground base

01:29:00.920 --> 01:29:02.960
inside Mount Hayes, Alaska.

01:29:03.460 --> 01:29:05.020
It had advanced technology,

01:29:05.560 --> 01:29:06.060
consoles,

01:29:06.800 --> 01:29:07.820
personnel that looked

01:29:07.820 --> 01:29:08.520
like military.

01:29:08.780 --> 01:29:10.060
He named three more bases,

01:29:10.560 --> 01:29:12.060
Mount Perdido in Spain,

01:29:12.380 --> 01:29:13.320
Mount Iñangani

01:29:13.320 --> 01:29:14.180
in Zimbabwe,

01:29:14.660 --> 01:29:15.280
Mount Zile

01:29:15.280 --> 01:29:16.140
in Australia.

01:29:16.620 --> 01:29:17.240
Years later,

01:29:17.420 --> 01:29:18.220
Joe McMonigle,

01:29:18.460 --> 01:29:20.160
another extremely talented

01:29:20.160 --> 01:29:20.840
remote viewer,

01:29:21.320 --> 01:29:22.880
was given the same coordinates

01:29:22.880 --> 01:29:23.420
blind.

01:29:23.900 --> 01:29:25.100
He saw the same mountains

01:29:25.100 --> 01:29:26.580
with the same underground

01:29:26.580 --> 01:29:27.440
command centers,

01:29:27.720 --> 01:29:29.180
and then he saw

01:29:29.180 --> 01:29:30.040
something else.

01:29:30.500 --> 01:29:31.680
The bases were connected

01:29:31.680 --> 01:29:33.400
like nodes of a network,

01:29:33.920 --> 01:29:35.160
and when he remote viewed

01:29:35.160 --> 01:29:36.720
Mount Perdido in Spain,

01:29:36.720 --> 01:29:38.660
he saw how it was built,

01:29:39.060 --> 01:29:40.540
not by non-human intelligence,

01:29:41.100 --> 01:29:41.880
but by us,

01:29:42.260 --> 01:29:42.860
helicopters,

01:29:42.860 --> 01:29:44.140
cargo crates,

01:29:44.740 --> 01:29:45.680
human personnel

01:29:45.680 --> 01:29:46.880
moving materials

01:29:46.880 --> 01:29:47.820
into the mountain.

01:29:48.280 --> 01:29:49.440
Is it really possible

01:29:49.440 --> 01:29:50.800
to see through

01:29:50.800 --> 01:29:51.840
someone else's eyes

01:29:51.840 --> 01:29:52.560
or sense through

01:29:52.560 --> 01:29:53.140
their senses?

01:29:53.700 --> 01:29:54.380
Actually,

01:29:54.660 --> 01:29:55.540
we're not sure

01:29:55.540 --> 01:29:56.540
exactly how it works,

01:29:56.660 --> 01:29:57.560
but it is possible

01:29:57.560 --> 01:29:59.540
to report on the position

01:29:59.540 --> 01:30:00.760
or place that they're located.

01:30:01.760 --> 01:30:03.300
Once a private company

01:30:03.300 --> 01:30:04.500
has reverse-engineered

01:30:04.500 --> 01:30:06.300
enough non-human technology,

01:30:06.840 --> 01:30:07.620
its capabilities

01:30:07.620 --> 01:30:09.000
can leap decades

01:30:09.000 --> 01:30:09.880
or centuries

01:30:09.880 --> 01:30:11.520
ahead of our own military.

01:30:11.520 --> 01:30:12.360
At that point,

01:30:12.440 --> 01:30:13.240
you're talking about

01:30:13.240 --> 01:30:14.400
a parallel civilization

01:30:14.400 --> 01:30:15.920
with its own cities,

01:30:16.340 --> 01:30:17.540
its own private armies.

01:30:18.020 --> 01:30:18.600
In physics,

01:30:18.760 --> 01:30:19.600
we won't discover

01:30:19.600 --> 01:30:20.840
for another century.

01:30:22.820 --> 01:30:24.340
People seem to disappear

01:30:24.340 --> 01:30:25.820
on all of these mountains.

01:30:26.340 --> 01:30:27.300
The mountains contain

01:30:27.300 --> 01:30:28.620
geomagnetic anomalies.

01:30:29.100 --> 01:30:30.120
UFOs appear,

01:30:30.700 --> 01:30:31.700
often coming in

01:30:31.700 --> 01:30:32.680
and out of the mountains.

01:30:33.400 --> 01:30:34.740
The mountains almost feel

01:30:34.740 --> 01:30:35.680
like an air pocket

01:30:35.680 --> 01:30:37.600
of a different consensus reality.

01:30:37.600 --> 01:30:38.640
As my friend

01:30:38.640 --> 01:30:40.420
and legendary UFO researcher

01:30:40.420 --> 01:30:41.840
Richard Dolan might say,

01:30:42.260 --> 01:30:43.640
a breakaway civilization.

01:30:44.540 --> 01:30:46.200
And this is the real takeaway.

01:30:46.480 --> 01:30:47.980
After years of researching

01:30:47.980 --> 01:30:49.040
this stuff myself,

01:30:49.220 --> 01:30:50.320
people always want to know

01:30:50.320 --> 01:30:51.380
how I shake out

01:30:51.380 --> 01:30:53.020
on what's actually going on

01:30:53.020 --> 01:30:54.520
with UFOs in the government.

01:30:54.680 --> 01:30:56.000
This is the stuff you get into

01:30:56.000 --> 01:30:57.800
that's just hard to talk about.

01:30:57.900 --> 01:30:58.560
It's hard to say

01:30:58.560 --> 01:30:59.620
with a straight face.

01:31:00.040 --> 01:31:01.020
Jointly operated

01:31:01.020 --> 01:31:02.740
human and non-human bases

01:31:02.740 --> 01:31:04.500
with entirely insulated

01:31:04.500 --> 01:31:06.420
and separate chains of command.

01:31:06.420 --> 01:31:08.160
I know that sounds nuts,

01:31:08.320 --> 01:31:09.860
but think about it another way.

01:31:10.280 --> 01:31:10.980
Name me a topic

01:31:10.980 --> 01:31:12.280
other than UFOs

01:31:12.280 --> 01:31:13.300
with this much

01:31:13.300 --> 01:31:14.720
circumstantial evidence,

01:31:14.960 --> 01:31:16.220
but nothing concrete

01:31:16.220 --> 01:31:16.880
and definitive.

01:31:17.240 --> 01:31:18.340
So much smoke,

01:31:18.500 --> 01:31:19.260
but no fire.

01:31:19.420 --> 01:31:20.280
The control system

01:31:20.280 --> 01:31:21.060
around this stuff

01:31:21.060 --> 01:31:22.560
has to operate

01:31:22.560 --> 01:31:23.920
parapsychologically.

01:31:24.160 --> 01:31:24.920
They have to have

01:31:24.920 --> 01:31:26.360
next-level abilities

01:31:26.360 --> 01:31:27.840
to cover themselves up.

01:31:27.940 --> 01:31:28.560
And if anyone

01:31:28.560 --> 01:31:30.060
is in charge of disclosure,

01:31:30.560 --> 01:31:31.120
they are.

01:31:31.680 --> 01:31:32.780
This is the truth

01:31:32.780 --> 01:31:33.820
behind some of these

01:31:33.820 --> 01:31:35.260
missing scientist cases.

01:31:35.260 --> 01:31:36.740
And it's the reason

01:31:36.740 --> 01:31:38.520
why certain technology trees

01:31:38.520 --> 01:31:40.480
involving gravity manipulation,

01:31:41.060 --> 01:31:42.000
nanotechnology,

01:31:42.540 --> 01:31:42.960
fusion,

01:31:43.180 --> 01:31:44.000
and free energy

01:31:44.000 --> 01:31:45.860
tend to hit dead ends

01:31:45.860 --> 01:31:47.720
or get softly enveloped

01:31:47.720 --> 01:31:49.420
by bizarre shell outfits.

01:31:49.660 --> 01:31:50.640
The tech going nowhere

01:31:50.640 --> 01:31:51.840
in the civilian world,

01:31:52.180 --> 01:31:53.220
but getting siphoned

01:31:53.220 --> 01:31:54.220
into the black.

01:31:56.900 --> 01:31:58.700
And think about it logically.

01:31:59.000 --> 01:31:59.880
To think that

01:31:59.880 --> 01:32:01.900
non-human intelligence exists,

01:32:01.900 --> 01:32:03.760
but hasn't infiltrated

01:32:03.760 --> 01:32:05.040
governments and private

01:32:05.040 --> 01:32:06.300
aerospace is maybe

01:32:06.300 --> 01:32:07.960
just as crazy as believing

01:32:07.960 --> 01:32:09.160
in non-human intelligence

01:32:09.160 --> 01:32:10.060
in the first place.

01:32:10.340 --> 01:32:11.540
You can't really be open

01:32:11.540 --> 01:32:12.920
to one and completely

01:32:12.920 --> 01:32:14.120
closed off to the other.

01:32:14.380 --> 01:32:15.600
If this is at all real,

01:32:15.960 --> 01:32:16.600
then of course,

01:32:16.860 --> 01:32:17.360
the government

01:32:17.360 --> 01:32:18.680
can't just disclose it.

01:32:19.020 --> 01:32:20.300
It's probably gonna get

01:32:20.300 --> 01:32:21.920
spoon-fed to us in fiction.

01:32:22.380 --> 01:32:23.420
How else do you prepare

01:32:23.420 --> 01:32:24.620
a world for the idea

01:32:24.620 --> 01:32:25.280
that the mountain

01:32:25.280 --> 01:32:26.100
on the horizon

01:32:26.100 --> 01:32:27.360
might not be a mountain

01:32:27.360 --> 01:32:27.960
at all?

01:32:27.960 --> 01:32:28.780
So yes,

01:32:28.920 --> 01:32:29.700
maybe Jake Barber

01:32:29.700 --> 01:32:30.960
didn't land another egg

01:32:30.960 --> 01:32:31.780
as he predicted

01:32:31.780 --> 01:32:32.900
when I interviewed him.

01:32:33.040 --> 01:32:33.760
We hope to do

01:32:33.760 --> 01:32:34.740
a demonstration

01:32:34.740 --> 01:32:37.400
and invite key members

01:32:37.400 --> 01:32:38.220
of the public

01:32:38.220 --> 01:32:39.160
from institutions

01:32:39.160 --> 01:32:40.620
and demonstrate this

01:32:40.620 --> 01:32:41.620
and maybe even get

01:32:41.620 --> 01:32:42.560
something to the ground.

01:32:44.020 --> 01:32:45.060
And his attempts

01:32:45.060 --> 01:32:46.280
to recreate legacy

01:32:46.280 --> 01:32:47.200
UFO efforts

01:32:47.200 --> 01:32:47.880
in a friendly,

01:32:48.080 --> 01:32:48.960
open-source way

01:32:48.960 --> 01:32:49.920
in the form of

01:32:49.920 --> 01:32:50.740
a private company

01:32:50.740 --> 01:32:51.800
called Skywatcher

01:32:51.800 --> 01:32:53.020
seems like it's

01:32:53.020 --> 01:32:53.900
hit some snags.

01:32:54.080 --> 01:32:54.860
But what if,

01:32:55.000 --> 01:32:55.640
in the tradition

01:32:55.640 --> 01:32:57.080
Tom DeLonge established

01:32:57.080 --> 01:32:57.780
with his book

01:32:57.780 --> 01:32:58.900
Secret Machines,

01:32:59.540 --> 01:33:00.300
Jake designed

01:33:00.300 --> 01:33:01.260
this manuscript,

01:33:01.560 --> 01:33:02.580
The Sentinels of Ether,

01:33:03.020 --> 01:33:04.680
to encode the real truth

01:33:04.680 --> 01:33:05.280
in fiction

01:33:05.280 --> 01:33:07.100
and then go on

01:33:07.100 --> 01:33:08.180
to use the Pentagon's

01:33:08.180 --> 01:33:09.500
own review process

01:33:09.500 --> 01:33:10.520
and redactions

01:33:10.520 --> 01:33:12.000
as authentication.

01:33:12.460 --> 01:33:13.520
If just two chapters

01:33:13.520 --> 01:33:15.420
of this Sentinels of Ether story

01:33:15.420 --> 01:33:17.080
that exists today online

01:33:17.080 --> 01:33:18.880
triggered a firestorm

01:33:18.880 --> 01:33:19.840
of black ink,

01:33:20.160 --> 01:33:20.960
what is hiding

01:33:20.960 --> 01:33:21.800
in the rest?

01:33:22.080 --> 01:33:23.280
What was redacted?

01:33:23.420 --> 01:33:24.900
If this sounds like fiction,

01:33:25.260 --> 01:33:25.800
then good,

01:33:25.800 --> 01:33:27.200
because that's exactly

01:33:27.200 --> 01:33:28.360
where they've been hiding it.

01:33:28.540 --> 01:33:29.240
In plain sight,

01:33:29.560 --> 01:33:30.440
wrapped in stories

01:33:30.440 --> 01:33:31.120
we were taught

01:33:31.120 --> 01:33:32.360
not to take seriously.

01:33:32.920 --> 01:33:34.180
And maybe that's the point.

01:33:34.400 --> 01:33:35.520
A reality this shattering

01:33:35.520 --> 01:33:36.500
can't be announced.

01:33:36.760 --> 01:33:38.040
It has to be drip-fed,

01:33:38.440 --> 01:33:39.560
encoded in movies,

01:33:39.860 --> 01:33:40.640
buried in books,

01:33:41.100 --> 01:33:42.540
disguised as entertainment

01:33:42.540 --> 01:33:43.620
until we're ready

01:33:43.620 --> 01:33:44.160
to see it

01:33:44.160 --> 01:33:45.420
for what it really is.

01:33:45.540 --> 01:33:46.220
We don't need

01:33:46.220 --> 01:33:46.980
a billion-dollar

01:33:46.980 --> 01:33:47.660
black budget,

01:33:47.920 --> 01:33:48.980
psionic handlers,

01:33:49.200 --> 01:33:50.100
or brain chips.

01:33:50.320 --> 01:33:51.520
We have the hardware,

01:33:51.940 --> 01:33:53.240
we have the brainwaves,

01:33:53.240 --> 01:33:54.640
and we have a love beam

01:33:54.640 --> 01:33:55.620
they can't jam.

01:33:55.800 --> 01:33:57.960
Eight billion biological antennas

01:33:57.960 --> 01:33:58.900
walking around

01:33:58.900 --> 01:33:59.600
on the surface

01:33:59.600 --> 01:34:00.520
of planet Earth.

01:34:00.640 --> 01:34:01.760
Homegrown receivers

01:34:01.760 --> 01:34:03.000
capable of connecting

01:34:03.000 --> 01:34:03.700
to a field

01:34:03.700 --> 01:34:04.860
the black world spent

01:34:04.860 --> 01:34:05.740
70 years

01:34:05.740 --> 01:34:07.020
trying to monopolize.

01:34:07.300 --> 01:34:08.240
Because there's a far

01:34:08.240 --> 01:34:09.340
more radical thesis

01:34:09.340 --> 01:34:09.840
than

01:34:09.840 --> 01:34:11.680
they're hiding UFOs.

01:34:11.760 --> 01:34:12.420
It's more like

01:34:12.420 --> 01:34:13.360
they're hiding us

01:34:13.360 --> 01:34:14.220
from ourselves.

01:34:14.820 --> 01:34:15.500
The technology

01:34:15.500 --> 01:34:16.820
isn't in the craft,

01:34:17.180 --> 01:34:18.240
it's in human neurology,

01:34:19.020 --> 01:34:20.240
and in the human spirit.

01:34:20.240 --> 01:34:21.200
And they've spent

01:34:21.200 --> 01:34:22.780
70 years making sure

01:34:22.780 --> 01:34:23.760
that we don't figure

01:34:23.760 --> 01:34:24.460
that out.

01:34:24.780 --> 01:34:25.740
Non-human intelligence

01:34:25.740 --> 01:34:26.500
doesn't need

01:34:26.500 --> 01:34:27.440
a press conference

01:34:27.440 --> 01:34:28.440
at the White House.

01:34:28.660 --> 01:34:29.700
They've been making contact

01:34:29.700 --> 01:34:30.960
through back channels,

01:34:31.340 --> 01:34:32.400
indigenous tribes,

01:34:32.740 --> 01:34:33.800
secret societies,

01:34:34.300 --> 01:34:35.360
occult practitioners,

01:34:36.120 --> 01:34:36.860
psychonauts,

01:34:37.360 --> 01:34:38.680
lone religious monks,

01:34:39.300 --> 01:34:40.400
or just some kid

01:34:40.400 --> 01:34:42.060
sending coherent love beams

01:34:42.060 --> 01:34:43.440
out his bedroom window.

01:34:44.600 --> 01:34:45.380
Sooner or later,

01:34:45.580 --> 01:34:46.800
something might pick up.

01:34:46.980 --> 01:34:48.200
In the words of Jake Barber,

01:34:48.400 --> 01:34:49.340
we're not alone.

01:34:49.340 --> 01:34:51.060
The skies aren't classified.

01:34:51.780 --> 01:34:52.280
Your conscience

01:34:52.280 --> 01:34:53.340
can't be redacted.

01:34:54.100 --> 01:34:55.080
I encourage us all

01:34:55.080 --> 01:34:55.880
to look upward

01:34:55.880 --> 01:34:56.780
and look inward

01:34:56.780 --> 01:34:57.860
and to become

01:34:57.860 --> 01:34:58.780
the best versions

01:34:58.780 --> 01:35:00.040
of ourselves quickly.

